OL,3,CHeadteacher charged after alleged
OL,4,Cattack on school site
OL,6,FA headteacher has been charged after
OL,7,Fan alleged attack at a school in Port
OL,8,FTalbot.
OL,10,FPolice were called to St Joseph's
OL,11,FCatholic School in Port Talbot at
OL,12,F9.50am on Wednesday, March 5 after
OL,13,Freports of an incident.
OL,15,FA 51-year-old man was taken to
OL,16,Fhospital with non-life threatening or
OL,17,Flife-changing injuries.
