OL,3,CHeadteacher charged after alleged
OL,4,Cattack on school site
OL,6,FSouth Wales police confirmed Anthony
OL,7,FFelton, 54, from Swansea had been
OL,8,Fcharged with Section 18- attempt
OL,9,Fwounding with intent in connection
OL,10,Fwith the alleged incident.
OL,12,FA spokesperson for the force said:
OL,13,F"The victim has been discharged from
OL,14,Fhospital with minor injuries."
OL,16,FFather-of-three Anthony Felton was
OL,17,Fappointed headteacher of the school in
OL,18,FMarch 2023.
